{"tid":1724941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發]大量五毛大軍殺入連登","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T16:32:45.000Z","uid":56966,"like":32,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"79817fa736cf3230a443bfe6a79b2dd7efb1a56f","tid":1724941,"uid":56966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:10:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢排真係多撚左好多五毛散水撚入侵連登亂帶風向</span><br />\n<br />\n守唔守唔洗冷氣軍師教，<strong>要教唔該上前線教</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該大家<strong>意志堅定啲</strong>，唔好俾人講兩句就動搖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋，屌你老母，下下叫前線克制要贏民意，我真係屌哂你班傻西，都咁耐仲未醒，依家都歸哂邊，大把人核爆都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講呢啲嘅唔係傻西左膠就係五毛，你唔諗下<strong>點撚解要克制讓步嘅唔係黑警同港共政府</strong>？邊個先係真暴力？裝修下死物就屌，殺人強姦濫權唔屌？<strong>原來死物重要過人命</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb62edfb1d443fb75b5c739823d3d636d225ef2e","tid":1724941,"uid":56966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdb8a05aa706657c64739d4c125dcb6c61dcab4","tid":1724941,"uid":56966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"唔好再俾五毛帶風向"},{"pid":"579807a518d500f358f56a194ba31196f0ddd042","tid":1724941,"uid":56966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:11:54.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"6a4565a9f4903b80517531d7c784921644f2bd79","tid":1724941,"uid":56966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:12:11.000Z","msg":"攬炒！！！"},{"pid":"0cf8683483b234e8acd0b922e5e01ac274c47092","tid":1724941,"uid":56966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:12:31.00